snippet.title: Liquidator 2: Welcome to Hell - Gameplay
snippet.description:
Part of my Obscure First Person Shooters series: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL2BBA1AB1CF53EEAC

Gameplay footage from Liquidator 2: Welcome to Hell. Actual gameplay begins at 3:37.

Remember that peculiar little Russian game built on the Build engine called Liquidator? Well, this is the sequel. However, it would probably more accurate to say that this is a near complete remake, believe it or not, right down to the identical level design, identical monsters, and even identical music. But it IS a sequel. You can see the "2" right there.
